# 🚦 Project Rules – BendyBeth V2

## 1. Styling
- Use **Tailwind CSS only** for all styling.
- All design tokens (colors, fonts, spacing, breakpoints) live in `tailwind.config.js`.
- `styles.css` should only contain:
  - `@tailwind base;`
  - `@tailwind components;`
  - `@tailwind utilities;`
  - Tiny helper classes if absolutely needed.
- ❌ Do not create extra CSS files (like primitives, semantic, alias, effects, etc.).
- ❌ Do not duplicate Tailwind utilities in CSS.

## 2. File & Folder Structure
